.TH "hw_device_state" 9 "hw_device_state" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
hw_device_state \- enables/disables interrupts (execute without interruption)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" hw_device_state
.BI "(struct ci_hdrc *ci "  ","
.BI "u32 dma "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ci" 12
the controller
.IP "dma" 12
0 => disable, !0 => enable and set dma engine
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function returns an error code
